data.description: Private, quiet, yet convenient location.  DiVosta built quality construction. Wonderful 2/2 split plan villa. Freshly painted Great Room with Bamboo flooring and Vaulted ceilings.  Granite counters & back splash in kitchen.  Interior Laundry.  Two master suites w/ sliders that open to a 20 x 20 private screened patio with garden setting. Enjoy outdoor living all year long. Additional storage room off the patio. Walk to the pool, tennis, local shopping & restaurants. HOA includes maintenance of the roof, exterior painting, cable, building insurance, common amenities, pool & tennis courts.
